High Performance Fuel Injectors

ASNU High Performance Fuel Injectors

This set of ASNU 1050cc are out the door on their way to a lucky customer

From 300cc to 1500cc we’ve got plenty of options for you with the worlds largest range of purpose built high performance fuel injectors

Our performance injectors feature our multi-hole orifice cap, cut using the latest laser technology for greater accuracy and repeatability. Using this technology allows us to produce injectors with specific spray patterns and flow rates to meet the customers’ exact requirements guaranteeing increased performance every time
